TITLE: Implementing a Message Consumer in C#
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates a simple implementation of a message consumer.  It consumes the `SubmitOrder` message type and publishes an `OrderSubmitted` message. It uses the `ConsumeContext` to access the message and publish a new message.
SOURCE: https://github.com/masstransit/masstransit/blob/develop/doc/content/3.documentation/1.concepts/2.consumers.md#2025-04-18_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
class SubmitOrderConsumer :
    IConsumer<SubmitOrder>
{
    public async Task Consume(ConsumeContext<SubmitOrder> context)
    {
        await context.Publish<OrderSubmitted>(new
        {
            context.Message.OrderId
        });
    }
}
```

