TITLE: Creating Bus with Transaction Middleware in C#
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to configure a MassTransit bus with transaction middleware to share a single committable transaction across consumers. This configuration includes settings for transaction timeout and isolation level.
SOURCE: https://github.com/masstransit/masstransit/blob/develop/doc/content/3.documentation/2.configuration/3.middleware/transactions.md#2025-04-18_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
