TITLE: Configuring Message Retry on a Specific Endpoint in MassTransit
DESCRIPTION: Setting up message retry on a manually configured receive endpoint, allowing for more granular control over retry policies for specific consumers or endpoints.
SOURCE: https://github.com/masstransit/masstransit/blob/develop/doc/content/3.documentation/1.concepts/4.exceptions.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
services.AddMassTransit(x =>
{
    x.AddConsumer<SubmitOrderConsumer>();

    x.UsingRabbitMq((context, cfg) =>
    {
        cfg.ReceiveEndpoint("submit-order", e =>
        {
            e.UseMessageRetry(r => r.Immediate(5));

            e.ConfigureConsumer<SubmitOrderConsumer>(context);
        });
    });
});
```

