TITLE: Testing Request/Response with MassTransit Test Harness
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the testing of a request/respond pattern using the MassTransit Test Harness. It sets up a handler for `SubmitOrder` requests and verifies responses, ensuring that the 'OrderResponse' has the expected status. Prerequisites include setting up MassTransit and the necessary service collection.
