TITLE: Configuring OnMissingInstance Behavior for Events (C#)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet details how to configure the behavior of a saga state machine when an event is received that does not correlate to an existing instance, allowing custom responses when no instance is found.
SOURCE: https://github.com/masstransit/masstransit/blob/develop/doc/content/3.documentation/2.configuration/1.sagas/2.event.md#2025-04-18_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
public record RequestOrderCancellation(Guid OrderId);
public record OrderNotFound(Guid OrderId);

public class OrderStateMachine :
    MassTransitStateMachine<OrderState>
{
    public OrderStateMachine()
    {
        Event(() => OrderCancellationRequested, e =>
        {
            e.CorrelateById(context => context.Message.OrderId);

