TITLE: Main Program Example with TransactionalEnlistmentBus in C#
DESCRIPTION: Provides an example of a Console App using a TransactionalEnlistmentBus to manage transactions around business logic and message publishing. The example ensures that the transaction is completed upon successful execution of commands.
SOURCE: https://github.com/masstransit/masstransit/blob/develop/doc/content/3.documentation/2.configuration/3.middleware/transactions.md#2025-04-18_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: csharp
