TITLE: Unit Testing with MassTransit and RabbitMQ
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates configuring MassTransit's test harness with RabbitMQ transport within a .NET test case. This snippet shows a basic RabbitMQ setup for testing a consumer with given credentials and broker address.
SOURCE: https://github.com/masstransit/masstransit/blob/develop/doc/content/4.support/4.upgrade.md#2025-04-18_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
[Test]
public async Task Should_use_broker()
{
    await using var provider = new ServiceCollection()
        .AddMassTransitTestHarness(x =>
        {
            x.AddConsumer<SubmitOrderConsumer>();

            x.UsingRabbitMq((context, cfg) =>
            {
                cfg.Host("some-broker-address", h =>
                {
                    h.Username("joe");
                    h.Password("cool");
                });

                cfg.ConfigureEndpoints(context);
            });
        })
        .BuildServiceProvider(true);
}
```

